29
00:01:15,590 --> 00:01:17,799
Then they offer them jobs, for example,

30
00:01:17,799 --> 00:01:19,999
at a so-called think tank in Shanghai.

31
00:01:19,999 --> 00:01:22,869
And once the foreigner takes the job,

32
00:01:22,869 --> 00:01:26,289
they’ll be expected to give up the secrets.

33
00:01:26,289 --> 00:01:28,679
Sounds sketchy and super illegal, sure.

34
00:01:28,679 --> 00:01:30,119
But you got to admit,

35
00:01:30,119 --> 00:01:31,340
it’s a pretty clever way to

36
00:01:31,340 --> 00:01:33,350
trick people into betraying their country:

37
00:01:33,350 --> 00:01:35,439
“Hey, it’s my job!

38
00:01:35,439 --> 00:01:38,119
I have to do it for money!”

39
00:01:38,119 --> 00:01:40,020
So far, we don’t know how many people

40
00:01:40,020 --> 00:01:43,100
this aggressive campaign has successfully
recruited.

41
00:01:43,100 --> 00:01:44,810
But this is something both British

42
00:01:44,810 --> 00:01:48,329
