emails ever.

51
00:02:11,830 --> 00:02:14,230
And incidentally, this is not the first time
LinkedIn

52
00:02:14,230 --> 00:02:17,420
has been at the center of some China controversy.

53
00:02:17,420 --> 00:02:20,500
When they went into the China market back
in 2014,

54
