56
00:02:26,909 --> 00:02:30,049
the Tiananmen Square Massacre or Falun Gong.

57
00:02:30,049 --> 00:02:33,340
Even if those users were in America.

58
00:02:33,340 --> 00:02:36,370
The modern world depends on technology in
space.

59
00:02:36,370 --> 00:02:37,370
For example,

60
00:02:37,370 --> 00:02:39,260
if it weren’t the GPS satellites

61
00:02:39,260 --> 00:02:41,260
