jousting.

65
00:02:49,530 --> 00:02:53,680
So, since we rely so much on GPS satellites...

66
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:56,150
this might be a problem.

67
00:02:56,150 --> 00:02:57,579
For years, China has been building up

68
00:02:57,579 --> 00:02:59,500
its anti-satellite capabilities.

69
