74
00:03:13,099 --> 00:03:14,360
The US, for its part,

75
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:16,819
has been falling behind China and Russia

76
00:03:16,819 --> 00:03:18,659
for the future of space warfare

77
00:03:18,659 --> 00:03:21,530
But really, these are exciting times.

78
00:03:21,530 --> 00:03:25,440
As a top official said, we’re in Cold War
2

79
00:03:25,440 --> 00:03:26,950
With an Arms Race 2

80
00:03:26,950 --> 00:03:29,400
With a Space Race 2

81
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:32,239
Now some might tell you this could all lead
to World War 3.

82
00:03:32,239 --> 00:03:33,879
But, really, that’s ridiculous.

83
00:03:33,879 --> 00:03:36,209
It will be Space Wars 1.

84
00:03:36,209 --> 00:03:38,010
I said “space wars”, Disney.

85
00:03:38,010 --> 00:03:40,030
You can’t sue me!

86
00:03:40,030 --> 00:03:41,700
But I wouldn’t want you to worry that

87
00:03:41,700 --> 00:03:45,559
we won’t still have warfare right here on
Earth, too.

88
00:03:45,559 --> 00:03:48,829
Because China may be also helping with that.

89
00:03:48,829 --> 00:03:49,849
China is helping to set up

90
00:03:49,849 --> 00:03:54,060
