95
00:04:02,469 --> 00:04:03,569
It’s a classic.

96
00:04:03,569 --> 00:04:06,980
It’s literally one of the four Chinese classics.

97
00:04:06,980 --> 00:04:10,480
Ok, back to Afghanistan...sadly.

98
00:04:10,480 --> 00:04:12,659
Now, supposedly,

99
00:04:12,659 --> 00:04:15,920
Chinese troops won’t actually be on Afghan
soil,

100
