101
00:04:18,810 --> 00:04:21,340
But despite that very believable denial,

102
00:04:21,340 --> 00:04:24,740
China has already paid for and started building
a training base

103
00:04:24,740 --> 00:04:28,060
for Afghan troops inside Afghanistan—

104
00:04:28,060 --> 00:04:29,680
in the the Wakhan Corridor,

105
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:33,870
which is next to China’s Xinjiang Autonomous
Region.

106
00:04:33,870 --> 00:04:35,390
Xinjiang is where the Communist Party

107
00:04:35,390 --> 00:04:39,020
has detained up to a million Muslims.

108
00:04:39,020 --> 00:04:42,190
Is this mountain brigade really about fighting
terrorism?

109
00:04:42,190 --> 00:04:45,810
Or is it more about cutting off any hope of
escape?

110
00:04:45,810 --> 00:04:47,340
Speaking of no escape,

111
00:04:47,340 --> 00:04:49,370
China’s State council has made it easy

112
00:04:49,370 --> 00:04:51,610
for the happy people of Macau, Hong Kong,

113
00:04:51,610 --> 00:04:55,550
and Taiwan to get Chinese residence cards—

114
00:04:55,550 --> 00:04:58,970
so they can live and/or work in mainland China.

115
00:04:58,970 --> 00:05:02,030
Surely there’s no sinister catch to this!

116
00:05:02,030 --> 00:05:04,280
Here’s the sinister catch.

117
00:05:04,280 --> 00:05:07,210
Misbehave, lose the card.

118
00:05:07,210 --> 00:05:10,270
That could spell trouble for say, Hong Kongers,

119
00:05:10,270 --> 00:05:13,960
who hold the incorrect view of democracy in
Hong Kong.

120
00:05:13,960 --> 00:05:17,970
Or Taiwanese who hold the incorrect view of
what a country is.

121
00:05:17,970 --> 00:05:20,210
Speaking of gradually eroding freedoms,

122
00:05:20,210 --> 00:05:23,740
