130
00:05:41,889 --> 00:05:44,100
Now I know that sounds controversial, but
don’t worry.

131
00:05:44,100 --> 00:05:47,120
The handover was done in a secret ceremony.

132
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:50,570
“The event was closed to press and neither
news media

133
